snippet.title: Chikn Nuggit Nightmare Fwiends - Trailer
snippet.description:
This is a teaser trailer to Chikn Nuggit Nightmare Fwiends by Alexander G. Gochev (alexgochev).

After the past months, i'm finally about to finish making my own horror game.

This game will release on February something, if it's possible.

Follow my game:
